   - Initial value: 28000000.00 (as of 2023-12-31)
   - End value: 33082821.36 (as of 2024-02-05)

2. This total can be decomposed into two component sub-items:
   - "Total Current Liabilities"
     - Initial value: 0.00
     - End value: 3143833.89
   
   - "Total Owner's Equity"
     - Initial value: 28000000.00
     - End value: 29938987.47

These two sub-items add up to the total liabilities and equity amount.
